title: Pearl Jam - Live at The Astoria (London)
description:
2006-04-20 Astoria, London, England,  UK
Rare bootleg of this epic concert.
The return of Pearl Jam to London, after 6 years. Performed at the legendary Astoria Theater, the place where Jimi Hendrix burned a guitar onstage for the first time, and that has been demolished in order to allow the construction of a new underground station. This concert was performed to guests only, including members of the english fan club, and proeminent english artists, such as Robert Plant and Ian Anderson.
First live performance of several songs, that were yet to be released at the album "Pearl Jam".
